item.title: Wealth Redefined: The Power of Being a Stay at Home Mum with Jasleen Chawla
item.description: This week, Sim chats with Jasleen about her journey from corporate life at Deloitte and Goldman Sachs to choosing the stay-at-home wife path and building her own platform on TikTok. They dive into money anxiety, navigating financial conversations in marriage, and why creating purpose outside of a 9–5 matters. With candid insights on feminism, career breaks, and financial independence, this episode is a refreshing look at redefining success on your own terms ... item.title: Oasis Queues, Kebabs & The Great Shower Debate
item.description:
On this week’s Vogue & Amber: Oasis weekend debrief - from Liam Gallagher’s moody face to bar scraps, missed songs and who went to bed first (very important info). Vogue interviews Davina McCall about her new TV show, while Amber sticks to kebabs and early nights.

Plus, hot takes on shower habits and sparkling water, spooky ghost stories, Sister Cards confessions and the wildest influencer fails (and wins) of the week... Feed: https://feeds.captivate.fm/spencer-vogue/
